OL,3,CCumbrian Labour MP calls for Keir
OL,4,CStarmer to step down
OL,6,FA Cumbrian MP has publicly called for
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer to step down.
OL,9,FFollowing the Prime Minister's speech
OL,10,Fon Monday Markus Campbell-Savours, the
OL,11,FLabour MP for Penrith and Solway, took
OL,12,Fto social media to say he felt that
OL,13,Fhis party needed a new leader.
OL,15,FHe said: "I have listened carefully to
OL,16,Fthe Prime Minister's speech. Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer is a decent, principled and
OL,18,Fkind man. But his leadership is not
OL,19,Fworking, and it is with genuine regret
OL,20,Fthat I say so.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778602269
OL,3,CCumbrian Labour MP calls for Keir
OL,4,CStarmer to step down
OL,6,F"His position is now untenable, and
OL,7,Fcolleagues should have the courage to
OL,8,Fsay publicly what many have said
OL,9,Fprivately for months."
OL,11,FIn the post on social media the MP
OL,12,Fsaid "loyalty matters" but "today
OL,13,Floyalty lies with our elected members
OL,14,Facross the country and with the 1,500
OL,15,Fwho lost their seats last week".
OL,17,FHe added: "It does not lie in
OL,18,Fmaintaining a course that is not
OL,19,Fcommanding confidence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778602269
OL,3,CCumbrian Labour MP calls for Keir
OL,4,CStarmer to step down
OL,6,F"What the Party needs now is
OL,7,Fleadership with a credible vision for
OL,8,Fthe country, a clear sense of
OL,9,Fdirection, purpose and ambition. Those
OL,10,Fskills exist within our ranks, and I
OL,11,Fam confident we can find a leader who
OL,12,Fhas them."
OL,14,FIn his speech on Monday, Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer vowed to prove his "doubters"
OL,16,Fwrong as he delivered a major address
OL,17,Faimed at averting a potential
OL,18,Fleadership challenge.
OL,26,@wD@\OUwD@eO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
