FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778602269
OL,3,CCumbrian Labour MP calls for Keir
OL,4,CStarmer to step down
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister promised sweeping
OL,7,Fchanges to tackle the "big challenges"
OL,8,Ffacing the UK, as he fought to save
OL,9,Fhis job following a bruising set of
OL,10,Flocal election results and subsequent
OL,11,Fcalls for his resignation.
OL,13,FDescribing Friday's results as tough,
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer claimed the country
OL,15,Fwas facing both "dangerous times" and
OL,16,F"dangerous opponents".
OL,18,F"If we don't get this right, our
OL,19,Fcountry will go down a very dark
OL,20,Fpath," claimed the PM.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778602269
OL,3,CCumbrian Labour MP calls for Keir
OL,4,CStarmer to step down
OL,6,F"I know people are frustrated by the
OL,7,Fstate of Britain, frustrated by
OL,8,Fpolitics, and some people, frustrated
OL,9,Fwith me," said Starmer.
OL,11,F"I know I have my doubters, I know I
OL,12,Fneed to prove them wrong, and I will."
OL,14,FIn December, Campbell-Savours had the
OL,15,FLabour whip suspended after voting
OL,16,Fagainst the government's original
OL,17,Fversion of plans to impose inheritance
OL,18,Ftax on farms.
OL,20,FHe had had the whip restored in March.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
